      Color Change Wrap Films

      Dual Layer, Cast Vinyl Colored Film

      1080

      3M Wrap Film Series 1080

      8900

      Ready to use right out of the box - with or without graphic protection. Features slideable and repositionable pressure-activated adhesive with non-visible air release channels. Removable.

      Printed Reflective Wrap Film

      Wrappable Reflective Vinyl Film

      780mC-10R

      3M Scotchlite Print Wrap Film 780mC-10R

      8518, 8519, 8548G, 8549L

      -Robust properties enable conformability
      -Heat recovery minimizes bruising
      -Reflectivity at wide viewing angles

      Vehicle Window Films

      Dual Layer, Perforated Cast Vinyl Film

      8170-P50

      3M Scotchcal Perforated Window Graphic Film 8170-P50, 3M Scotchcal Perforated Window Graphic Film 8170-P40

      8914, 8518

      As a cast vinyl, offers excellent lifting resistance and durability. Offered with 50/50 or 60/40 perforation pattern.

      Vehicle Window Films

      Calendered Vinyl Perforated Film

      IJ67

      3M Scotchcal Perforated Window Film IJ67

      8518, 8914

      -60/40 perforation pattern
      -Removable adhesive for easy updates
      -For budget-minded, short-term applications

      E-Cut Graphic Material

      Calendered Vinyl Colored Film

      SC50

      3M Scotchcal Graphic Film Series SC50

      1920DR, 9740i

      3-mil intermediate films designed for electronic cutting and thermal transfer. Excellent cutting and weeding and removable adhesive. Flat and simple curves.

      E-Cut Graphic Material

      Cast Vinyl Colored Film

      7725
      7125

      3M Scotchcal ElectroCut Graphic Film Series 7725/7125

      1920DR, 9740i

      2-mil premium films designed for electronic cutting and thermal transfer. 7725 moisture-resistant synthetic liner lays flat and won't split. Flat and flat with rivets.

      Vehicle Window Films

      Cast Vinyl Optically Clear Film

      IJ8150

      3M Scotchcal Clear View Graphic Film IJ8150

      8914, 8518

      Optical clarity with excellent printability in a durable and even conformable film. Print unique effects, even see-through images.

      Full Printed Vehicle Wrap Film

      Cast Vinyl Metallic Film

      IJ180mC-120

      3M Print Wrap Film IJ180mC-120

      8518, 8519, 8548G, 8549L, 8528, 8900

      Industry favorite for wraps, 130% stretch, optimized initial tack, slideability, air release and snap-up
